sellerAgent.name: Your Home Sold Guaranteed Realty - Kings of Real Estate Team

data.description: Price improvement! Fantastic location! Motivated seller! Make this home Yours now. Move-in ready, with a functional layout, charming ranch on a flat corner lot. This home has a beautiful wood-burning fireplace in the living room that is great for family gatherings. The living room, kitchen, dining room, hallway, and bathrooms have wood grain tile planks. Custom tile shower in the main bath and American Standard jetted tub in the second bath. The backyard is fenced-in. The seller is offering $1000 credit to replace carpets in 3 bedrooms.
